data.description: BEAUTIFUL HOME IN THE CENTER OF CASSELBERRY OFF THE 17TH HOLE. HOME HAS 4 BEDROOMS 2 FULL BATHROOMS. 1/2 BATHROOM IN COMMON AREA OF HOME. STUNNING MARBLE FIREPLACE. HARDWOOD FLOORS, MARBLE FLOORS AND TILE. SPLIT FLOOR PLAN WITH MASTER BEDROOM AND SPARE BEDROOM ON ONE SIDE. 2 BEDROOMS 1 FULL BATHROOM ON OTHER SIDE. HOME IS ALMOST 2500 SQUARE FEET. SCREENED IN LARGE PATIO OVERLOOKING GOLF COURSE. NEWER ROOF, PLUS SOLAR WAS JUST ADDED. IT HAS NATURAL GAS ALONG WITH ELECTRICAL POWER. HOME ALSO HAS EAT IN KITCHEN, FORMAL LIVING ROOM AND DINING ROOM. LARGE FAMILY ROOM.INSIDE LAUNDRY ROOM. LARGE 2 CAR GARAGE. SELLERS ARE VERY MOTIVATED.     BUYERS MUST VERIFY ROOM SIZES.
